"{\"uid\": \"si.com-fannation-boxing-italian-boxer-withdraws-early-in-controversial-paris-olympic-match-01j49v8x32fd\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Mohamed Bahaa  In a brief yet dramatic encounter at the Paris Olympics, Italy's Angela Carini withdrew from her bout against Algeria's Imane Khelif after just 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"score\": 0.8289799738709216, \"rank\": 0.20630006140030702, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 96, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 128, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999995436856939, \"rank\": 4.552811980267429e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 138, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif, who was previously banned from the 2023 World Championships for failing a gender eligibility test, dominated the match, leading Carini to end the fight prematurely.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9827173762676414, \"rank\": 0.01758656573084404, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Italian boxer signaled her coach, Emanuel Renzini, that she could not continue due to severe pain from Khelif\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s punches.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"score\": 0.6571510509534256, \"rank\": 0.44563566082348494, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite Renzini\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s encouragement to endure until the round's end, Carini halted the fight again after another punch.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9827173762676414, \"rank\": 0.01758656573084404, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s too strong,\\\" Renzini recalled her saying.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini, visibly emotional, apologized to her supporters, expressing regret over the fight's short duration.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9827173762676414, \"rank\": 0.01758656573084404, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had entered the ring to fight,\\\" she said in Italian.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"score\": 0.6571510509534256, \"rank\": 0.44563566082348494, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not give up, but a punch hurt too much and so I said enough.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I go out with my head held high.\\\"\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's dominant performance rekindled debates on whether she and Chinese Taipei's Lin Yu-ting should compete in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\", \"score\": 0.9888446655653038, \"rank\": 0.009642807681402918, \"text\": \"Taipei\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\"}, {\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both were disqualified from the 2023 World Championships under International Boxing Association (IBA) rules prohibiting athletes with XY chromosomes in women's events.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9977519896501345, \"rank\": 0.0022530504405583692, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC), however, has taken a more lenient approach, allowing them to compete in Paris, stating, \\\"They are women in their passports.\\\"\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1212, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999960046808, \"rank\": 3.995308586827572e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark Adams, IOC spokesperson, defended the decision, highlighting the athletes' long history in the sport.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298826524, \"rank\": 0.45833333333321225, \"text\": \"Mark Adams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These athletes competed many times before for many years.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t just suddenly arrive.\\\"\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA, in a statement, maintained their stance on the disqualifications based on thorough reviews and expressed concerns over the IOC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s differing regulations.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1585, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9977519896501345, \"rank\": 0.0022530504405583692, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s differing regulations on these matters, in which IBA is not involved, raise serious questions about both competitive fairness and athletes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 safety,\\\" the statement read.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1806, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9977519896501345, \"rank\": 0.0022530504405583692, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif, who avoided reporters post-fight, received strong support from Algeria's Olympic committee, which condemned foreign media for targeting her.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999995436856939, \"rank\": 4.552811980267429e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Such attacks on her personality and dignity are deeply unfair, especially as she prepares for the pinnacle of her career at the Olympics,\\\" their statement read.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Italian officials had questioned the fairness of Khelif\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s participation prior to the fight.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"score\": 0.6571510509534256, \"rank\": 0.44563566082348494, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Renzini revealed that many had pressured Carini not to fight, warning of the potential danger.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2376, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9827173762676414, \"rank\": 0.01758656573084404, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite this, Renzini chose a diplomatic stance on Khelif's eligibility.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not my decision,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would not want to be in those shoes because I think it's a very difficult decision.\\\"\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s journey to the Olympics has been marked by significant obstacles.\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in rural Algeria, she defied local norms to pursue boxing, traveling long distances and funding her training through scrap metal sales and her mother's couscous business.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2722, \"end\": 2729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999995436856939, \"rank\": 4.552811980267429e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her dedication led to notable successes, including a fifth-place finish at the Tokyo Olympics and a silver medal at the 2022 World Championships.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The power behind Khelif\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s punches was evident in her bout with Mexico\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Brianda Tamara in December 2022.\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamara described the fight as the most painful in her 13-year career, even compared to sparring with men.\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The debate surrounding Khelif\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s eligibility is likely to continue as she advances in the competition.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Carini, who previously paused her career after her father's death before her Tokyo match, faces another Olympic challenge as she prepares for her next bout.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3362, \"end\": 3368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9827173762676414, \"rank\": 0.01758656573084404, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 3439, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999984125314635, \"rank\": 1.5874711188555237e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not up to me to decide,\\\" Carini said, reflecting on the broader implications of her fight against Khelif.\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3553, \"end\": 3559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9827173762676414, \"rank\": 0.01758656573084404, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations    \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 4100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4033, \"end\": 4051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.735440503117269e-17, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 